<script>
  import { h, resolveDynamicComponent } from 'vue';

  function Icon(props, ctx) {
     const Component = resolveDynamicComponent(`icon-${props.icon}`); //icon图标
    //const Component = resolveDynamicComponent(`${props.icon}`);
    return h(Component);
  }
  export default Icon;
</script>
